# Hand Gesture Recognition using SVM

## Project Overview
This project implements a Hand Gesture Recognition system using Machine Learning.
The model classifies different hand gestures from image data using an SVM classifier.

## Dataset
Dataset Used:
LeapGestRecog Dataset

## Technologies Used
- Python
- OpenCV
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Scikit-learn

## Machine Learning Algorithm
- Support Vector Machine (SVM)

## Features
- Image preprocessing
- Gesture classification
- Confusion matrix visualization
- Prediction visualization
- Accuracy evaluation

## Folder Structure
SCT_ML_4/
│
├── leapGestRecog/
├── main.py
├── confusion_matrix.png
├── predictions.png
└── README.md

## Installation

Install required libraries:

pip install numpy opencv-python matplotlib scikit-learn

## Run Project

python main.py

## Output
- Classification Report
- Accuracy Score
- Confusion Matrix
- Predicted Gesture Images

